<h2 id="heading-26">The Solution: Professional Bookkeeping</h2>

<p>The only way to catch and prevent these mistakes is with dedicated bookkeeping attention. Here's what that looks like:</p>

<h3 id="heading-27">Monthly Bookkeeping Service</h3>

<ul>
<li><strong>Reconciliation:</strong> All accounts reconciled monthly</li>
<li><strong>Review:</strong> Transaction categorization and error checking</li>
<li><strong>Reports:</strong> Profit & loss, balance sheet, cash flow</li>
<li><strong>Tax planning:</strong> Quarterly tax strategy reviews</li>
</ul>

